Subject: [PATCH 129/194] dt-bindings: input: touchscreen: st,stmfts: Introduce
 reset GPIO

FTS has associated reset GPIO, document it.

Signed-off-by: David Heidelberg <david@ixit.cz>
---
 .../devicetree/bindings/input/touchscreen/st,stmfts.yaml      | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/input/touchscreen/st,stmfts.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/input/touchscreen/st,stmfts.yaml
index 12256ae7df90..64c4f24ea3dd 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/input/touchscreen/st,stmfts.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/input/touchscreen/st,stmfts.yaml
@@ -40,6 +40,10 @@ properties:
   vdd-supply:
     description: Power supply
 
+  reset-gpios:
+    description: Reset GPIO (active-low)
+    maxItems: 1
+
 required:
   - compatible
   - reg
